channel.title: Auxy Forum Awards (2017) - Winners!
channel.description:
Welcome to the :a:UXY FORUM AWAR :b:S (2017) - That's enough chit-chat.... you voted & the winners this year are:
**BEST AUXY TRACK** =
>**WINNER: <ins>Apprentice Angel on Shooting Star Hill by DJ Totto - Kayasho Remix</ins> - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/kayashokayasho/itorinormxkayasho)** >2. Kleuren by Conux - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/conux_official/kleuren) >3. Catalyst by Mr Anderson - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/mrandersonauxy/catalyst) >4. Changes by aUstin Haga - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/austin_haga/changes) >5. Shatter by aUstin Haga - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/austin_haga/shatter) > > .~-----![Kay|45x45](upload://ku6rFIeUC2yVdjxxpdA16aMkFXS.jpg)-----![Conux|45x45](upload://32TntYMiF1xB2DlTewWE25ulA66.jpg)-----![Anderson|45x45](upload://ahNwyJMLbjuKL6p63gbSwmSC8Gt.jpg)-----![Haga|45x45](upload://sfeFZ8jXVGT7CXFxPBhTD0LHw6t.jpg)-----![Haga|45x45](upload://sfeFZ8jXVGT7CXFxPBhTD0LHw6t.jpg)-----~'
**BEST AUXY PRODUCER** = >**WINNER - 1st Equal: <ins>aUstin Haga</ins> - [Soundcloud](https://soundcloud.com/austin_haga)** >**WINNER - 1st Equal: <ins>Decruz</ins> - [Soundcloud](https://soundcloud.com/decruz-182260894)** >3. Moemx - [Soundcloud](https://soundcloud.com/moemx) >4. NEWNAMES - [Soundcloud](https://soundcloud.com/newnames) >5. Southborne - [Soundcloud](https://soundcloud.com/southborne) > >.~----- [ ![Decruz|45x45](upload://aEp4q58obtPOnvoaMQOdIaCPVZH.jpg)![Haga|45x45](upload://sfeFZ8jXVGT7CXFxPBhTD0LHw6t.jpg) ]-----![Moemx|45x45](upload://7DitdJ6xzpgeZuZvLz20GPj4k2q.jpg)-----![NewNames|45x45](upload://8LSTCYKt7roQ8r59GP3KoKtlPvr.jpg)-----![Southborne|45x45](upload://n0GijWRe0lbbGDnBO0PQgOUOgBE.jpg)-----~' > > **Other finalists:** Bradley Saint James (BSJ), Produk, Conux, Andrew Adams & Gargoyle.
**MOST SUPPORTIVE FORUM MEMBERS** = >**WINNER: <ins>Southborne</ins>** >2. HAYVN >3. Stereofield >4. Mr Mooo >5. Voltt > >.~-----![Southborne|45x45](upload://n0GijWRe0lbbGDnBO0PQgOUOgBE.jpg)----- ![HAYVN|45x45](upload://nF8K6ymwDgYa36RvSZQZ5jFKN0A.jpg)-----![Stereofield|45x45](upload://4rFYFojHBaBYv4mi2MUSXopX4Y6.jpg)-----![Mr Mooo|45x45](upload://ctw9QVCo7iRW6ZJGa26ivEVY1tl.jpg)-----![Voltt|45x45](upload://VHY9lBUNTKAM2Iq6t9qkvd1Dos.png)-----~' > > **Other finalists:** Produk, GOD/Phil, Kerfuffle, Stigmo & Indigoo.
**CONGRATULATIONS** to all of the winners, finalists & nominees! The top :five: in each category win a beautiful, rare & highly exclusive pink unicorn. And the winners of Track / Producer categories will be promoted in the official Auxy feed.
Special thanks to everyone who nominated, voted and/or contributed to the Auxy Disco forum this year.
Thanks to @Auxy and @xavior for their help.
And we should all take a moment to remember [Richard](http://bit.ly/18gECvy).
I've been your Awards host and janitor, @MisterMaster - Thanks for being a great community. The winners and nominees are outstanding, but there's also many other excellent forum members who have produced amazing, innovative and unique sounds this year. **Merry Christmas** to you all! Look forward to hearing your new Auxy releases in 2018.
